dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. At head of title: Madeira. Includes cross section of shoreline. "Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty, Jany. 3rd, 1845." "1689."
dct_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dct_publisher_sm: London : Published ... at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the Admiralty charts, 21 Poultry, and Royal Exchange East, 1845.
